//Setting up for Mobile Development
Install Grunt and Grunt-Cli
Install Xcode
Install Cordova
Install Ionic
clone repo from github
NPM install
bower install

//cordova plugin commands
cordova plugin list
cordova plugin remove 'name of plugin'


//complete restart on ios
exit xcode
ionic platform remove ios
ionic platform add ios
ionic build ios
open project in xcode
cordova prepare

//rebuild in ios after changes:
grunt build:ios
open in xcode
click play > triggers build, install, run
